llm_solution_answer:
\begin{aligned}
&\text{General small–amplitude precession (epicyclic) frequency:}\quad
\Omega^{2}=3\,\omega^{2}-\frac{q_{0}}{m}\,\left.\frac{dE(r)}{dr}\right|_{r=r_{0}}.
\\[6pt]
&\text{For the rotating isothermal plasma (with }k=\omega^{2}/(2k_{B}T_{0})\text{), using }E(r)=\dfrac{C\,\Delta f(r)}{r},\;
\Delta f(r)=\frac{e^{m_{i}kr^{2}}-1}{e^{m_{i}kR^{2}}-1}-\frac{e^{m_{e}kr^{2}}-1}{e^{m_{e}kR^{2}}-1},
\\
&\text{and the circular–orbit condition }q_{0}E(r_{0})=-m\omega^{2}r_{0},
\text{ one obtains the explicit result (independent of }q_{0}\text{):}
\\[4pt]
&\qquad\Omega^{2}=\omega^{2}\left[
2
+
2r_{0}^{2}\,
\frac{
m_{i}k\,\dfrac{e^{m_{i}k r_{0}^{2}}}{e^{m_{i}k R^{2}}-1}
-
m_{e}k\,\dfrac{e^{m_{e}k r_{0}^{2}}}{e^{m_{e}k R^{2}}-1}
}{
\dfrac{e^{m_{i}k r_{0}^{2}}-1}{e^{m_{i}k R^{2}}-1}
-
\dfrac{e^{m_{e}k r_{0}^{2}}-1}{e^{m_{e}k R^{2}}-1}
}
\right].
\end{aligned}

